{"tid":1147444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）老翁養兒40年始知非親生　怒極殺妻跳河自盡","createTime":"2019-05-10T00:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T08:17:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2013cca442d9553c72d63c1c14137b91317a08fe","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190509/photo/bkn-20190509140418254-0509_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190509141247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190509%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190509140418254-0509_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190509141247&h=0e1a8e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n湖北黃石市70歲黃姓老翁早前懷疑袁姓妻子出軌，為兒子做親子鑑定後，證實兒子並非親生，近日與妻子爭執後將其殺死，其後跳河自殺。<br />\n<br />\n經當地警方調查，黃翁育有一子一女，兒子今年已40歲。在得知兒子非親生骨肉後，黃翁多次向袁妻及子女提出分家要求，並多次發生爭執。上月19日黃翁再次與妻子爭吵，黃一氣之下將對方殺死並逃離現場。<br />\n<br />\n家屬發現後報警，惟袁婦因失血過多，當場死亡。及後，警方發現黃逃往江北方向，同月24日在蘄春縣一村鎮江邊發現其遺物。4天後警方在江邊發現一具無名男屍，經檢驗及DNA比對，確認是黃翁。"},{"pid":"ce5e6a41bc7f0a10b396abdc7f106d30bfd4ff90","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190509/mobile/bkn-20190509140418254-0509_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190509%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190509140418254-0509_00952_001.html&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGgfwWQc8qO99IFO6%2BGFOovI%3D&h=c4c2774e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190509/mobile/bkn-20190509140418254-0509_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d910304f5f865221a686ecda538a8d7249704cf8","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T00:26:49.000Z","msg":"【支那邏輯】【直播跳河】男主播溺斃 拍攝者：同佢認識20分鐘竟要賠$5.8萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1033739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1033739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"04ef19df000d05d85d823c5501d79d21c6906ffe","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T01:19:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d58e4f3d0c286c8954d0735dea2dbc58663fb08","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea6110e78cbe188c6319d0c105c1e80ac8319e9","tid":1147444,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:17:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}